keyMappings:
unmap x
unmap X

map y copyCurrentUrl
map p openCopiedUrlInNewTab

map d removeTab
map u restoreTab
map C createTab
map R reload hard

map h previousTab
map l nextTab
map < moveTabLeft
map > moveTabRight

map <c-h> scrollLeft
map <c-l> scrollRight

map J scrollPageDown
map K scrollPageUp

map ,p togglePinTab
map <c-`> visitPreviousTab

map s Vomnibar.activate keyword=gs
map t Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map z Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map O Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map S Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=gs
map T Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab

map [ goPrevious
map ] goNext
searchEngines:
a: https://www.amazon.com/s/?field-keywords=%s Amazon

gs: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google Search
gf: https://www.google.com/search?&tbm=fin&q=%s Google Finance
gd https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/search?q=%s Google Drive

imdb: http://www.imdb.com/find?q=%s IMDB

ll: https://lucidlife.wordpress.com/?s=%s LucidLife

reddit: https://www.reddit.com/search?q=%s Reddit

sb https://stackblitz.com/fork/%s

tpb: https://thepiratebay.rocks/search/%s TPB

yt: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s YouTube

wiki: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
